channel.title: Changing Filament :: CID guide website
channel.description: To change filament, navigate to the Filament button on the home screen by rotating the dial, and pressing the dial to select. There you will be presented with 4 options, Load, Unload, Change, and Purge. Load will let you load a filament into the printer. Follow the instructions on the screen. Unload will let you unload the currently stored filament. Follow the instructions on the screen.
